1
00:00:12,140 --> 00:00:16,840
[August 17, 2012]

2
00:00:31,350 --> 00:00:31,920
Move!

3
00:00:46,750 --> 00:00:47,610
Take them away!

4
00:00:48,280 --> 00:00:49,070
Anyone else here?

5
00:00:49,070 --> 00:00:50,560
Bring all detainees to the vehicle.

6
00:00:50,560 --> 00:00:51,070
Report!

7
00:00:51,090 --> 00:00:52,860
Armed drug dealers spotted
in the northwest corner.

8
00:00:52,860 --> 00:00:53,990
Requesting backup.

9
00:01:09,200 --> 00:01:09,710
Talk.

10
00:01:10,430 --> 00:01:12,289
Are you hiding something from me?

11
00:01:35,370 --> 00:01:36,620
You're Zhou Chuan.

12
00:01:37,550 --> 00:01:38,620
Who are you?

13
00:01:39,340 --> 00:01:40,940
I have no grudge against you.

14
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:42,400
I didn't want to kill you,

15
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:44,210
but someone wants you dead.

16
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:48,110
Come on out.

17
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:49,620
Verify the target.

18
00:01:53,770 --> 00:01:57,130
[Zhou Chuan, Vice Captain, SWAT team
of Haizhou Public Security Bureau]

19
00:01:57,700 --> 00:02:00,470
[8.17 Case]

20
00:03:18,930 --> 00:03:24,690
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

21
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:27,410
[Episode 1]

22
00:03:44,630 --> 00:03:48,150
[Zhou Jin, Officer, Security Management
Brigade of Nancheng Branch, Haizhou City]

23
00:03:56,030 --> 00:03:56,680
Brother.

24
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:58,790
I just hope that

25
00:03:59,310 --> 00:04:01,560
my future life would be smooth and easy,

26
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:03,730
like a straight river,

27
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:05,540
without wind or waves.

28
00:04:05,940 --> 00:04:08,060
Only smooth sailing.

29
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:11,120
Life is supposed to be difficult.

30
00:04:12,030 --> 00:04:13,890
Nothing is certain in this world.

31
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:15,420
Live in the moment.

32
00:04:16,070 --> 00:04:17,560
The feelings you have right now

33
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:18,760
are what matter most.

34
00:04:19,839 --> 00:04:21,430
Alright, stop overthinking.

35
00:04:21,430 --> 00:04:22,760
I'll always be here for you.

36
00:04:22,760 --> 00:04:23,880
Awesome!

37
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:33,800
Zhou Chuan.

38
00:04:34,630 --> 00:04:35,950
He was the top sniper

39
00:04:36,110 --> 00:04:38,260
of Haizhou City's SWAT team.

40
00:04:38,960 --> 00:04:41,170
He died in the line of duty
during the 8.17 Case.

41
00:04:41,170 --> 00:04:44,900
[Jiang Hansheng, Researcher, Criminal Research
Office, Binjiang Province Public Security]

42
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:44,159
His Type 92 service pistol and the killer

43
00:04:44,510 --> 00:04:45,630
are both missing.

44
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:47,880
At the scene, he was shot twice.

45
00:04:46,880 --> 00:04:52,500
[Personal Information: Zhou Chuan]

46
00:04:48,750 --> 00:04:50,720
One bullet hit his calf,

47
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:52,430
immobilizing him.

48
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:55,070
Another bullet hit the back of his head

49
00:04:55,070 --> 00:04:56,270
at a 45-degree angle,

50
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:57,430
from top to bottom.

51
00:04:58,000 --> 00:05:00,250
His abdomen was stabbed
more than 10 times.

52
00:05:00,250 --> 00:05:01,980
Even without those 2 gunshots,

53
00:05:02,290 --> 00:05:03,950
he would have died on the spot.

54
00:05:24,620 --> 00:05:25,130
Come in.

55
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:28,340
Professor.

56
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,480
The comparison results are in.

57
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:31,390
The DNA of the perpetrator

58
00:05:31,390 --> 00:05:33,050
found on Zhou Chuan's clothes

59
00:05:33,190 --> 00:05:35,060
matches perfectly with the DNA

60
00:05:34,230 --> 00:05:37,420
[Wang Pengze, Director, Criminal Research
Office, Binjiang Province Public Security]

61
00:05:35,080 --> 00:05:36,070
from the 1997 Huaiguang Case.

62
00:05:36,070 --> 00:05:37,270
It's the same person.

63
00:05:37,310 --> 00:05:39,710
We can investigate the cases together now.

64
00:05:42,670 --> 00:05:44,670
I know what you're concerned about.

65
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,530
Jiang Hansheng.

66
00:05:47,580 --> 00:05:49,900
I haven't agreed to let you

67
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:51,600
resume investigation work.

68
00:05:51,950 --> 00:05:53,409
This is not your business.

69
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:54,800
You can leave now.

70
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:56,200
Close the door after you.

71
00:05:56,500 --> 00:05:58,090
I will submit an appeal in my own name

72
00:05:58,090 --> 00:05:59,870
to the Provincial High Procuratorate

73
00:05:59,870 --> 00:06:02,800
to request a reinvestigation
of the Huaiguang case.

74
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:07,970
Jiang Hansheng.

75
00:06:09,100 --> 00:06:11,060
Am I speaking in a foreign language?

76
00:06:11,060 --> 00:06:13,190
Don't you understand what I'm saying?

77
00:06:13,580 --> 00:06:16,310
This is not the time for you to show off.

78
00:06:18,310 --> 00:06:18,970
Professor.

79
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:21,700
I'm not trying to show off.

80
00:06:22,750 --> 00:06:24,200
Since it's the same person,

81
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:25,950
the profile from the Huaiguang Case

82
00:06:25,950 --> 00:06:27,630
also applies to the 8.17 Case.

83
00:06:28,510 --> 00:06:30,270
The killer has long lacked affection,

84
00:06:30,270 --> 00:06:31,430
so he could have easily developed

85
00:06:31,430 --> 00:06:33,430
histrionic personality disorder.

86
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:35,190
If I were him,

87
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:37,560
I would definitely use various channels

88
00:06:37,560 --> 00:06:39,220
to monitor police movements.

89
00:06:39,830 --> 00:06:40,630
If necessary,

90
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:43,640
I would even give an irrelevant testimony.

91
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:44,560
This way,

92
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:46,360
I could observe these fools

93
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:48,630
I've been playing with up close.

94
00:06:49,830 --> 00:06:50,870
So I want to appear

95
00:06:50,870 --> 00:06:52,070
on a legal TV program.

96
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:58,480
Are you planning to challenge

97
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:01,750
the murderer on television?

98
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:07,520
Welcome to Legal Knowledge in Action.

99
00:07:07,650 --> 00:07:09,510
Today we have invited

100
00:07:09,510 --> 00:07:12,160
a young expert in criminal psychology,

101
00:07:12,180 --> 00:07:13,040
Officer Jiang.

102
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:16,040
Officer Jiang will use real cases

103
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:18,020
to discuss psychology with us...

104
00:07:20,220 --> 00:07:23,720
[2017]

105
00:07:24,790 --> 00:07:28,180
[Haizhou City]

106
00:07:29,960 --> 00:07:33,370
[Zhou Jin and Jiang Hansheng's first date]

107
00:07:31,100 --> 00:07:33,159
It's not that you're not good enough;

108
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:36,190
it's just that I'm not keen
on dating right now.

109
00:07:36,190 --> 00:07:37,510
You just don't want to date me.

110
00:07:37,510 --> 00:07:38,120
No.

111
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:39,270
I want to focus on my work.

112
00:07:39,270 --> 00:07:40,750
So you'd rather work than date me.

113
00:07:40,750 --> 00:07:41,390
No.

114
00:07:42,390 --> 00:07:43,240
Because I know

115
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:44,710
you're looking for marriage.

116
00:07:44,710 --> 00:07:47,040
So I need to think this through carefully.

117
00:07:47,070 --> 00:07:48,630
Think carefully about how to reject me.

118
00:07:48,630 --> 00:07:49,190
No.

119
00:07:49,870 --> 00:07:51,080
You shouldn't interpret it that way.

120
00:07:51,080 --> 00:07:52,110
You're such a good catch.

121
00:07:52,110 --> 00:07:53,720
There must be many girls
who would like you.

122
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:54,770
Just not you.

123
00:07:55,650 --> 00:07:56,730
We can be friends.

124
00:07:57,750 --> 00:07:59,409
At most, I'm your backup plan.

125
00:08:01,250 --> 00:08:02,510
What's wrong with you?

126
00:08:03,010 --> 00:08:05,070
I answered your questions properly.

127
00:08:05,370 --> 00:08:06,000
Why did you twist

128
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:07,160
everything I say?

129
00:08:08,070 --> 00:08:08,680
I'm sorry.

130
00:08:10,350 --> 00:08:12,210
I shouldn't have said it out loud.

131
00:08:12,350 --> 00:08:14,000
Shouldn't have said it out loud?

132
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:16,260
No, you shouldn't have thought that way.

133
00:08:17,950 --> 00:08:21,270
It's just that everything you've said
matches the "heartless girl" quotebook.

134
00:08:21,270 --> 00:08:22,560
What quotebook?

135
00:08:23,270 --> 00:08:25,040
You said you wanted to talk to me.

136
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:26,870
I had a feeling
you were going to reject me.

137
00:08:26,870 --> 00:08:28,270
So I looked it up online.

138
00:08:28,730 --> 00:08:29,360
I'm sorry.

139
00:08:45,090 --> 00:08:46,400
The one who should be apologizing

140
00:08:46,400 --> 00:08:47,400
is me.

141
00:08:48,030 --> 00:08:49,030
I really

142
00:08:49,050 --> 00:08:50,180
thought I could do this.

143
00:08:50,180 --> 00:08:51,510
I wanted to give it a try.

144
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:53,320
But after trying, I realized

145
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:54,390
I couldn't.

146
00:08:55,390 --> 00:08:57,670
Maybe I just don't know
how to date someone anymore.

147
00:08:57,670 --> 00:08:58,270
I'm sorry.

148
00:08:59,270 --> 00:09:00,270
It's all my fault.

149
00:09:01,790 --> 00:09:03,050
Say whatever you want.

150
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:03,680
It's okay.

151
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:08,080
Zhou Jin.

152
00:09:09,550 --> 00:09:11,270
It's not that you don't know how to love.

153
00:09:11,270 --> 00:09:12,890
You just don't know
how to handle arranged dates.

154
00:09:12,890 --> 00:09:14,320
A stranger sits in front of you

155
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:15,910
and says he wants to marry you.

156
00:09:15,910 --> 00:09:17,840
Not only can't you get excited about it,

157
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:19,370
but you also find it absurd.

158
00:09:19,670 --> 00:09:21,440
You prefer genuine excitement.

159
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:23,000
You only know how to be passionate,

160
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:23,870
focused,

161
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:25,860
and deeply committed in love.

162
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:27,050
Because you know

163
00:09:28,030 --> 00:09:29,940
what we have isn't love.

164
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:32,750
Rationally, you think

165
00:09:32,750 --> 00:09:34,510
you should be of the age to get married.

166
00:09:34,510 --> 00:09:36,590
You want to reassure your family,

167
00:09:36,910 --> 00:09:38,790
but you don't know how to skip over love

168
00:09:38,790 --> 00:09:40,240
and go straight to marriage.

169
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:41,480
So the more we meet,

170
00:09:41,510 --> 00:09:43,170
the more panicked you become.

171
00:09:43,390 --> 00:09:44,440
But I can see that

172
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:46,120
you're already trying very hard

173
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:47,780
every time you come to meet me.

174
00:09:48,640 --> 00:09:49,370
Rejecting me

175
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:52,070
is you respecting your own heart.

176
00:09:58,320 --> 00:09:58,960
I'm sorry.

177
00:09:59,790 --> 00:10:02,050
I shouldn't have analyzed you like this.

178
00:10:05,850 --> 00:10:06,420
Okay.

179
00:10:07,620 --> 00:10:08,420
I understand.

180
00:10:10,400 --> 00:10:11,230
I'll go now.

181
00:10:20,140 --> 00:10:21,070
Jiang Hansheng!

182
00:10:22,790 --> 00:10:24,050
I just said a few words.

183
00:10:24,630 --> 00:10:26,690
You didn't have to jump into the lake.

184
00:10:27,820 --> 00:10:29,220
I forgot we were on a boat.

185
00:10:37,500 --> 00:10:39,700
This paper needs to be spread out to dry.

186
00:10:40,100 --> 00:10:41,230
This is useless now.

187
00:10:42,880 --> 00:10:46,190
30 Reasons Why Jiang Hansheng Is
Perfect for Zhou Jin.

188
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:50,610
Is this how you pursue girls in general?

189
00:10:50,610 --> 00:10:51,600
I've never pursued a girl before.

190
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:53,330
So the girls pursued you instead?

191
00:10:53,330 --> 00:10:54,530
I don't believe that.

192
00:10:54,720 --> 00:10:55,950
I've never been in a relationship.

193
00:10:55,950 --> 00:10:56,990
That's impossible.

194
00:10:56,990 --> 00:10:57,590
It's true.

195
00:10:58,150 --> 00:10:59,280
My heart rate is low.

196
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:01,450
I rarely feel that flutter in my heart.

197
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:03,130
Do you feel it for me?

198
00:11:14,550 --> 00:11:15,740
Let me take a look.

199
00:11:15,920 --> 00:11:17,250
What did you write here?

200
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:19,300
Physical compatibility.

201
00:11:19,790 --> 00:11:22,150
Perfect height difference.

202
00:11:26,360 --> 00:11:28,220
Compatible age and zodiac signs.

203
00:11:28,230 --> 00:11:30,230
Compatible fortune and horoscope.

204
00:11:30,630 --> 00:11:32,090
Had genetic testing done.

205
00:11:32,210 --> 00:11:33,060
Good genes.

206
00:11:33,590 --> 00:11:35,920
You've really done your research online.

207
00:11:35,950 --> 00:11:38,210
Attitude: Dating with marriage in mind.

208
00:11:38,210 --> 00:11:40,740
Decision-making: Always prioritizing you.

209
00:11:45,520 --> 00:11:47,050
You value emotions deeply.

210
00:11:48,010 --> 00:11:49,440
You need someone

211
00:11:51,050 --> 00:11:53,510
who takes relationships just as seriously.

212
00:11:55,130 --> 00:11:56,060
I am that person.

213
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:07,540
I don't have much confidence in dating

214
00:12:07,540 --> 00:12:08,940
because I've failed before.

215
00:12:07,640 --> 00:12:12,970
[Zhou Jin and Jiang Hansheng's second date]

216
00:12:09,510 --> 00:12:10,530
I had

217
00:12:10,790 --> 00:12:12,640
a boyfriend

218
00:12:13,510 --> 00:12:14,870
for many years.

219
00:12:15,940 --> 00:12:17,200
Are you still in touch?

220
00:12:24,470 --> 00:12:26,070
How long have you been apart?

221
00:12:27,010 --> 00:12:27,760
Two years.

222
00:12:30,750 --> 00:12:31,550
Five years.

223
00:12:35,520 --> 00:12:37,250
His name is Jiang Cheng, right?

224
00:12:52,290 --> 00:12:53,220
If you can let go,

225
00:12:53,380 --> 00:12:54,180
then I can too.

226
00:13:01,110 --> 00:13:03,570
[2012]

227
00:13:03,590 --> 00:13:06,000
[Longwan Hotel]

228
00:13:06,030 --> 00:13:11,160
[10 days after the 8.17 operation]

229
00:13:12,240 --> 00:13:13,170
Police! Open up!

230
00:13:13,790 --> 00:13:14,790
Police! Don't move!

231
00:13:14,790 --> 00:13:15,460
Freeze!

232
00:13:15,500 --> 00:13:16,170
Stay still!

233
00:13:16,190 --> 00:13:17,390
Let me explain first.

234
00:13:18,150 --> 00:13:19,100
Put your clothes on.

235
00:13:19,100 --> 00:13:20,160
What's your name?

236
00:13:21,990 --> 00:13:22,830
Jiang Cheng.

237
00:13:47,130 --> 00:13:48,680
Due to the absence

238
00:13:48,700 --> 00:13:50,440
of a father figure in his birth family,

239
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:52,390
the killer developed extreme insecurity

240
00:13:52,390 --> 00:13:53,990
and a desperate need for love

241
00:13:54,260 --> 00:13:55,120
and attention.

242
00:13:55,600 --> 00:13:56,660
I also believe that

243
00:13:57,080 --> 00:13:58,810
he was abandoned by his mother.

244
00:13:59,510 --> 00:14:01,290
He considers himself an artist,

245
00:14:01,290 --> 00:14:02,660
using an artistic facade

246
00:14:02,660 --> 00:14:03,920
to cover up his crimes.

247
00:14:04,510 --> 00:14:05,630
These victims

248
00:14:05,680 --> 00:14:07,520
are merely substitutes for him.

249
00:14:08,390 --> 00:14:09,150
It's clear

250
00:14:09,660 --> 00:14:10,540
that mentally,

251
00:14:10,760 --> 00:14:12,290
he has experienced trauma.

252
00:14:13,700 --> 00:14:14,500
I believe

253
00:14:14,850 --> 00:14:16,400
defining him as a psychopath

254
00:14:16,400 --> 00:14:17,860
isn't entirely accurate.

255
00:14:17,880 --> 00:14:20,300
However, he does possess
traits of this personality type.

256
00:14:20,300 --> 00:14:22,030
How should we understand this?

257
00:14:22,960 --> 00:14:25,080
In medicine, there is a scale

258
00:14:25,080 --> 00:14:25,970
for assessing psychosis,

259
00:14:25,970 --> 00:14:27,630
called the Hare's Checklist.

260
00:14:27,650 --> 00:14:29,510
It includes 20 assessment items.

261
00:14:29,550 --> 00:14:29,880
For example,

262
00:14:29,880 --> 00:14:31,610
whether they appear charming,

263
00:14:31,630 --> 00:14:33,830
have strong manipulative tendencies,

264
00:14:33,880 --> 00:14:36,030
or have a limit to the range
of emotions they receive,

265
00:14:36,030 --> 00:14:37,510
which is what we commonly call

266
00:14:37,510 --> 00:14:38,640
the lack of empathy.

267
00:14:39,480 --> 00:14:40,120
Also,

268
00:14:40,280 --> 00:14:42,000
if they have
a grandiose sense of self-worth,

269
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:43,760
are pathological liars,
or have a series of other

270
00:14:43,760 --> 00:14:44,960
personality traits.

271
00:14:45,260 --> 00:14:46,330
I believe that

272
00:14:46,360 --> 00:14:47,960
if the Red Dress serial killer

273
00:14:47,960 --> 00:14:49,620
were to take this assessment,

274
00:14:49,640 --> 00:14:51,480
he would score high in many areas.

275
00:14:51,480 --> 00:14:52,610
But there's one item

276
00:14:52,840 --> 00:14:53,960
that he would score low on.

277
00:14:53,960 --> 00:14:54,960
Which one?

278
00:14:56,030 --> 00:14:57,640
Limited emotional range.

279
00:14:58,260 --> 00:14:59,720
Because, on the contrary,

280
00:14:59,760 --> 00:15:01,220
his emotions are intense.

281
00:15:01,260 --> 00:15:02,190
Strong emotions

282
00:15:02,290 --> 00:15:02,960
are what drove him to kill

283
00:15:02,960 --> 00:15:04,810
and stage the crime scenes.

284
00:15:05,460 --> 00:15:07,970
From how meticulously
he planned the murders,

285
00:15:07,970 --> 00:15:09,420
he appears to be calm

286
00:15:09,440 --> 00:15:10,500
and cold-blooded.

287
00:15:10,580 --> 00:15:12,640
But the drive behind his violent acts

288
00:15:13,030 --> 00:15:14,640
comes from being triggered.

289
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:16,360
Because deep inside,

290
00:15:16,670 --> 00:15:19,000
he's still a child with emotional trauma.

291
00:15:40,640 --> 00:15:41,700
They took the bait.

292
00:15:45,240 --> 00:15:46,570
Keep a close eye on them.

293
00:15:56,580 --> 00:15:57,240
Don't move.

294
00:15:58,320 --> 00:15:59,720
Move, and I'll shoot you.

295
00:16:02,800 --> 00:16:03,530
Let me go!

296
00:16:28,440 --> 00:16:29,570
Tie his hands.

297
00:16:35,640 --> 00:16:36,360
Tie him up.

298
00:16:41,530 --> 00:16:42,650
Who sent you?

299
00:16:43,690 --> 00:16:45,140
Our target isn't in the car.

300
00:16:45,140 --> 00:16:46,940
Keep following the GPS tracker.

301
00:16:54,130 --> 00:16:54,990
Officer Jiang.

302
00:16:55,750 --> 00:16:57,150
You've never even met me.

303
00:16:57,530 --> 00:16:59,930
How can you be so confident
that you know me?

304
00:17:32,460 --> 00:17:35,060
[2017]

305
00:17:34,640 --> 00:17:35,490
Jin.

306
00:17:35,950 --> 00:17:37,750
How are things going with Jiang?

307
00:17:36,620 --> 00:17:41,810
[Zhou Jin and Jiang Hansheng's third date]

308
00:17:37,990 --> 00:17:39,990
If it's a good match, settle it soon.

309
00:17:40,110 --> 00:17:43,440
Bring him home and give your dad something
to be happy about.

310
00:17:43,710 --> 00:17:44,800
Robbery!

311
00:17:45,140 --> 00:17:46,180
Run!

312
00:17:46,430 --> 00:17:47,150
Get away!

313
00:17:47,150 --> 00:17:47,990
We're being robbed!

314
00:17:47,990 --> 00:17:48,840
He has a gun!

315
00:17:51,910 --> 00:17:52,510
Freeze!

316
00:18:14,650 --> 00:18:15,310
Don't move!

317
00:18:26,240 --> 00:18:26,870
Zhou Jin!

318
00:18:27,160 --> 00:18:27,690
Zhou Jin!

319
00:18:28,390 --> 00:18:28,910
The gun.

320
00:18:29,680 --> 00:18:30,440
Get him.

321
00:18:30,940 --> 00:18:31,830
It's a replica.

322
00:18:31,860 --> 00:18:32,860
Not a real Type 92.

323
00:18:33,610 --> 00:18:34,250
Arrest...

324
00:18:34,860 --> 00:18:35,710
Arrest him.

325
00:18:35,730 --> 00:18:37,030
He's already under arrest.

326
00:18:37,030 --> 00:18:37,650
Don't worry.

327
00:18:37,650 --> 00:18:38,910
Zhou Jin, are you okay?

328
00:18:39,240 --> 00:18:42,070
Don't tell my parents.

329
00:18:42,640 --> 00:18:43,640
I won't tell them.

330
00:18:44,890 --> 00:18:45,950
Don't fall asleep!

331
00:18:46,460 --> 00:18:47,990
Family members can't go in.

332
00:18:48,080 --> 00:18:48,800
Zhou Jin.

333
00:18:55,720 --> 00:18:58,470
[Operation Room]

334
00:19:04,430 --> 00:19:05,060
Doctor.

335
00:19:05,230 --> 00:19:05,750
Hello.

336
00:19:05,780 --> 00:19:07,760
Let me brief you
on the patient's condition.

337
00:19:07,760 --> 00:19:08,890
She has 3 broken ribs

338
00:19:08,930 --> 00:19:10,130
and a cranial injury.

339
00:19:10,200 --> 00:19:11,930
The surgery carries some risk.

340
00:19:12,420 --> 00:19:13,930
We need a family member's signature.

341
00:19:13,930 --> 00:19:14,660
Is that okay?

342
00:19:15,260 --> 00:19:15,860
I'll sign.

343
00:19:15,940 --> 00:19:16,760
I am a family member.

344
00:19:16,760 --> 00:19:18,140
Okay, here.

345
00:19:44,800 --> 00:19:45,730
I'm done eating.

346
00:19:45,860 --> 00:19:46,590
Are you full?

347
00:20:06,950 --> 00:20:08,010
Let's get married.

348
00:20:13,750 --> 00:20:14,620
Once I'm discharged,

349
00:20:14,620 --> 00:20:16,820
we'll go get our marriage certificate.

350
00:20:19,410 --> 00:20:21,140
Have you thought this through?

351
00:20:22,350 --> 00:20:23,040
Just now.

352
00:20:25,650 --> 00:20:26,580
Jiang Hansheng.

353
00:20:28,790 --> 00:20:29,880
I'm serious.

354
00:20:36,190 --> 00:20:38,390
But we haven't been together that long.

355
00:20:38,540 --> 00:20:40,670
The length of time we've been together

356
00:20:40,730 --> 00:20:42,460
doesn't really mean anything.

357
00:20:42,990 --> 00:20:44,120
I've figured it out.

358
00:20:45,570 --> 00:20:46,900
Life is unpredictable,

359
00:20:48,600 --> 00:20:50,330
so we need to live in the moment.

360
00:20:53,190 --> 00:20:55,320
I trust what I'm feeling right now.

361
00:21:02,640 --> 00:21:03,640
Don't you want to?

362
00:21:03,950 --> 00:21:04,750
Of course I do.

363
00:21:07,080 --> 00:21:08,940
I'm just afraid you'll regret it.

364
00:21:09,710 --> 00:21:10,390
I won't.

365
00:21:13,980 --> 00:21:15,290
What if he comes back for you someday?

366
00:21:15,290 --> 00:21:15,980
He won't.

367
00:21:18,670 --> 00:21:19,310
Okay.

368
00:21:20,480 --> 00:21:21,540
Let's get married.

369
00:21:23,390 --> 00:21:24,360
Don't hurt me.

370
00:21:29,110 --> 00:21:30,110
Don't betray me.

371
00:21:34,080 --> 00:21:34,750
I won't.

372
00:21:36,240 --> 00:21:36,800
Zhou Jin,

373
00:21:38,280 --> 00:21:39,120
I promise you.

374
00:21:40,210 --> 00:21:41,100
I won't hurt you

375
00:21:42,040 --> 00:21:43,110
or betray you.

376
00:22:08,010 --> 00:22:08,540
Zhou Jin.

377
00:22:11,510 --> 00:22:12,380
Do you like me?

378
00:22:17,990 --> 00:22:18,590
It's okay.

379
00:22:19,310 --> 00:22:20,910
No need to answer right away.

380
00:22:25,190 --> 00:22:25,880
Hansheng.

381
00:22:48,280 --> 00:22:48,970
I

382
00:22:54,870 --> 00:22:55,870
trust you.

383
00:23:11,150 --> 00:23:11,910
Come on,

384
00:23:11,960 --> 00:23:12,820
Officer Jiang.

385
00:23:14,420 --> 00:23:15,700
Let's talk about

386
00:23:16,240 --> 00:23:17,220
your girl.

387
00:23:31,110 --> 00:23:32,910
The killer has been shot dead,

388
00:23:33,740 --> 00:23:36,020
but Zhou Chuan's gun is still missing.

389
00:23:36,910 --> 00:23:38,910
The case has to be suspended for now.

390
00:23:39,090 --> 00:23:40,850
For your protection,

391
00:23:41,450 --> 00:23:42,840
once you've recovered,

392
00:23:43,320 --> 00:23:46,850
the organization will arrange
for you to teach at a university.

393
00:23:53,840 --> 00:23:55,950
Protect...

394
00:23:56,210 --> 00:23:57,860
Zhou Jin.

395
00:23:59,820 --> 00:24:03,710
I need to protect Zhou Jin.

396
00:24:09,360 --> 00:24:12,630
[Tomb of the Martyr, Zhou Chuan]

397
00:24:17,880 --> 00:24:18,670
Brother,

398
00:24:20,080 --> 00:24:21,360
I've missed you.

399
00:24:43,090 --> 00:24:43,980
Door unlocked.

400
00:24:44,010 --> 00:24:45,090
Welcome home.

401
00:24:48,030 --> 00:24:51,550
[Zhou Jin, Investigator, Criminal Investigation
Brigade of Haizhou City, Nancheng Branch]

402
00:25:58,680 --> 00:25:59,230
Dan.

403
00:25:59,620 --> 00:26:00,150
Zhou Jin.

404
00:26:00,430 --> 00:26:02,150
A female body was found
downstream of the Tong River.

405
00:26:02,150 --> 00:26:03,060
I'll send you the location.

406
00:26:03,060 --> 00:26:04,260
Get there as soon as possible.

407
00:26:04,260 --> 00:26:04,650
Okay.

408
00:26:04,670 --> 00:26:05,800
I'll be right there.

409
00:26:11,430 --> 00:26:12,040
Door unlocked.

410
00:26:12,040 --> 00:26:13,080
Welcome home.

411
00:26:15,740 --> 00:26:16,200
You're leaving?

412
00:26:15,930 --> 00:26:18,260
[Jiang Hansheng, Associate Professor,
Haizhou University of Political Science and Law]

413
00:26:17,230 --> 00:26:18,660
Just got a call from the team.

414
00:26:18,660 --> 00:26:19,520
There's a case.

415
00:26:19,670 --> 00:26:20,390
It's fine.

416
00:26:20,410 --> 00:26:21,210
I understand.

417
00:26:21,360 --> 00:26:22,750
I'm really sorry.

418
00:26:22,750 --> 00:26:23,910
We had plans today

419
00:26:24,040 --> 00:26:25,770
to set up our new home together.

420
00:26:26,670 --> 00:26:28,270
But that's just how my job is.

421
00:26:28,470 --> 00:26:29,010
It can't be helped.

422
00:26:29,010 --> 00:26:31,410
I have to be ready
for assignments anytime.

423
00:26:45,250 --> 00:26:45,800
Zhou Jin.

424
00:26:46,410 --> 00:26:47,940
Do you like this apartment?

425
00:26:49,130 --> 00:26:49,780
It's nice.

426
00:26:52,750 --> 00:26:53,550
It's very you.

427
00:26:54,470 --> 00:26:54,990
Neat

428
00:26:55,710 --> 00:26:56,320
and calm.

429
00:27:01,230 --> 00:27:02,430
Do you really like it?

430
00:27:03,990 --> 00:27:04,560
I do.

431
00:27:06,320 --> 00:27:07,040
I really need to go now.

432
00:27:07,040 --> 00:27:07,670
I'm running late.

433
00:27:07,670 --> 00:27:08,340
I'll take you.

434
00:27:08,340 --> 00:27:08,800
No need.

435
00:27:08,890 --> 00:27:09,890
I can go by myself.

436
00:27:35,980 --> 00:27:36,560
Move along.

437
00:27:36,560 --> 00:27:37,080
Nothing to see here.

438
00:27:37,080 --> 00:27:38,280
Step back, everyone.

439
00:27:48,910 --> 00:27:49,640
Age:

440
00:27:50,080 --> 00:27:51,290
Under 25.

441
00:27:51,710 --> 00:27:52,670
Time of death?

442
00:27:52,040 --> 00:27:54,480
[Lu Pengfei, Investigator, Criminal
Investigation Brigade of Nancheng Branch]

443
00:27:53,400 --> 00:27:54,720
About 3 to 4 days ago.

444
00:27:54,750 --> 00:27:55,970
Set up the police tape in front.

445
00:27:55,970 --> 00:27:56,890
Please step back.

446
00:27:56,890 --> 00:27:57,990
We're investigating a case.

447
00:27:57,990 --> 00:27:59,680
Everyone, please move back.

448
00:27:59,970 --> 00:28:00,520
Make way.

449
00:28:00,520 --> 00:28:01,800
No talking.

450
00:28:00,540 --> 00:28:03,710
[Zhao Ping, Investigator, Criminal
Investigation Brigade of Nancheng Branch]

451
00:28:02,150 --> 00:28:03,430
Keep quiet.

452
00:28:03,560 --> 00:28:04,150
Senior.

453
00:28:05,140 --> 00:28:05,580
What?

454
00:28:05,630 --> 00:28:06,740
There are too many people here.

455
00:28:06,740 --> 00:28:08,490
Extend the police tape further out.

456
00:28:08,490 --> 00:28:09,620
Zhao Ping, help her.

457
00:28:09,620 --> 00:28:10,420
Be tactful.

458
00:28:10,450 --> 00:28:11,020
Got it.

459
00:28:11,640 --> 00:28:12,550
Let's go, Senior.

460
00:28:12,550 --> 00:28:13,730
Let's set up the police tape.

461
00:28:13,730 --> 00:28:14,190
Come on.

462
00:28:15,750 --> 00:28:16,470
Move along.

463
00:28:16,470 --> 00:28:17,670
Step back, step back.

464
00:28:17,710 --> 00:28:17,990
Here.

465
00:28:17,990 --> 00:28:18,800
Move back, move back.

466
00:28:18,800 --> 00:28:19,520
Please make way.

467
00:28:19,520 --> 00:28:20,360
Step back a bit.

468
00:28:20,360 --> 00:28:21,230
There's nothing to see here.

469
00:28:21,230 --> 00:28:22,430
It'll only upset you.

470
00:28:22,770 --> 00:28:23,640
Back up.

471
00:28:24,190 --> 00:28:25,390
Pull it further back.

472
00:28:25,750 --> 00:28:27,060
Everyone should keep an eye out

473
00:28:27,060 --> 00:28:28,390
for any missing persons

474
00:28:28,390 --> 00:28:29,390
or suspicious individuals around you.

475
00:28:29,390 --> 00:28:30,790
Call the police anytime.

476
00:28:32,690 --> 00:28:34,980
I heard the girl died horribly.

477
00:28:35,310 --> 00:28:37,240
Seems like she was shot in the head.

478
00:28:37,670 --> 00:28:39,280
A swimmer found her.

479
00:28:39,390 --> 00:28:41,390
No idea where she drifted from.

480
00:28:41,880 --> 00:28:42,950
Quiet down.

481
00:28:43,360 --> 00:28:45,160
Can we confirm the time of death?

482
00:28:45,250 --> 00:28:46,180
About 3 days ago.

483
00:28:46,880 --> 00:28:48,750
The gunshot wound
is the only fatal injury.

484
00:28:48,750 --> 00:28:50,210
Judging from the caliber,

485
00:28:50,880 --> 00:28:51,600
it should be...

486
00:28:51,600 --> 00:28:53,060
Is it from a Type 92 pistol?

487
00:28:53,520 --> 00:28:56,980
Let's wait for the autopsy results
for further confirmation.

488
00:28:58,990 --> 00:29:01,640
The forensic and trace evidence reports
are out.

489
00:29:01,640 --> 00:29:02,640
We can now confirm

490
00:29:02,840 --> 00:29:04,080
it came from Zhou Chuan's gun.

491
00:29:03,290 --> 00:29:07,470
[Tan Shiming, Captain, Criminal Investigation
Brigade of Nancheng Branch, Haizhou City]

492
00:29:04,770 --> 00:29:05,530
The 8.17 Case

493
00:29:06,510 --> 00:29:07,440
can now proceed.

494
00:29:09,260 --> 00:29:09,720
Report.

495
00:29:11,270 --> 00:29:11,830
Get out.

496
00:29:12,550 --> 00:29:13,410
Close the door.

497
00:29:26,800 --> 00:29:27,930
Stay 10 meters away.

498
00:29:32,920 --> 00:29:34,010
It won't work.

499
00:29:34,530 --> 00:29:35,970
Zhou Jin isn't suitable.

500
00:29:36,600 --> 00:29:37,190
Besides,

501
00:29:37,320 --> 00:29:38,040
she should recuse herself

502
00:29:38,040 --> 00:29:39,560
from this case.

503
00:29:39,930 --> 00:29:41,780
I'm not assigning her to the 8.17 Case.

504
00:29:41,780 --> 00:29:43,800
I'm assigning her to the
Tong River Corpse Case.

505
00:29:43,800 --> 00:29:45,730
But the murder weapon in that case

506
00:29:45,870 --> 00:29:47,530
is connected to the 8.17 Case.

507
00:29:47,600 --> 00:29:48,830
If you let her investigate,

508
00:29:48,830 --> 00:29:50,430
won't she figure it out soon?

509
00:29:50,720 --> 00:29:52,800
So I believe she'll give it her all.

510
00:29:52,970 --> 00:29:54,430
Yes, she definitely will.

511
00:29:54,440 --> 00:29:55,300
Let me tell you,

512
00:29:55,360 --> 00:29:57,280
just the numbers "8.17" are enough

513
00:29:57,280 --> 00:29:59,280
for her to put in her maximum effort.

514
00:30:03,840 --> 00:30:04,430
Besides,

515
00:30:05,470 --> 00:30:07,040
she just got married.

516
00:30:07,430 --> 00:30:08,750
Why do you have to make her

517
00:30:08,750 --> 00:30:10,600
lead the charge at this time?

518
00:30:12,220 --> 00:30:13,090
She's married?

519
00:30:13,990 --> 00:30:15,040
Just recently.

520
00:30:17,640 --> 00:30:19,500
I agree with everything you said.

521
00:30:19,560 --> 00:30:21,160
But I just have one question.

522
00:30:21,720 --> 00:30:23,240
Is she qualified enough?

523
00:30:25,600 --> 00:30:26,360
Well...

524
00:30:26,990 --> 00:30:28,190
She's young

525
00:30:28,840 --> 00:30:30,100
and lacks experience.

526
00:30:30,170 --> 00:30:32,840
She has never handled
any major cases independently.

527
00:30:32,840 --> 00:30:33,150
So...

528
00:30:33,150 --> 00:30:34,770
No one cares more about solving

529
00:30:34,770 --> 00:30:36,290
the 8.17 Case than her.

530
00:30:48,140 --> 00:30:48,830
Come in.

531
00:30:57,120 --> 00:30:57,710
Sir.

532
00:30:58,640 --> 00:31:00,700
What was all that rush about earlier?

533
00:31:03,120 --> 00:31:04,150
I know.

534
00:31:04,910 --> 00:31:05,880
I'm

535
00:31:06,320 --> 00:31:07,040
young,

536
00:31:07,390 --> 00:31:08,320
inexperienced,

537
00:31:08,950 --> 00:31:10,950
and haven't solved any major cases.

538
00:31:14,750 --> 00:31:16,550
I told you to stay 10 meters away.

539
00:31:16,910 --> 00:31:18,370
Who told you to eavesdrop?

540
00:31:18,670 --> 00:31:19,880
I wasn't eavesdropping.

541
00:31:19,880 --> 00:31:20,730
You weren't?

542
00:31:21,080 --> 00:31:22,340
You said that about me?

543
00:31:24,440 --> 00:31:25,170
No, I didn't.

544
00:31:28,270 --> 00:31:29,960
I want to investigate
the Tong River Corpse Case.

545
00:31:29,960 --> 00:31:30,560
See, see?

546
00:31:30,750 --> 00:31:31,990
You still claim you weren't eavesdropping?

547
00:31:31,990 --> 00:31:33,390
I really wasn't.

548
00:31:34,910 --> 00:31:36,280
I simply believe

549
00:31:36,470 --> 00:31:37,210
that these types of

550
00:31:37,210 --> 00:31:39,190
violent crimes against female victims

551
00:31:39,190 --> 00:31:40,990
are better handled by female officers.

552
00:31:40,990 --> 00:31:42,520
The victim had no ID,

553
00:31:42,750 --> 00:31:44,600
and we couldn't match
any useful information.

554
00:31:44,600 --> 00:31:47,120
We definitely need
more officers for canvassing.

555
00:31:47,120 --> 00:31:48,720
I can certainly contribute.

556
00:31:49,040 --> 00:31:50,640
It's not because of that gun?

557
00:31:52,520 --> 00:31:54,180
Is it really my brother's gun?

558
00:31:55,040 --> 00:31:56,230
No comment.

559
00:31:57,880 --> 00:31:58,560
Sir,

560
00:31:58,840 --> 00:32:00,560
is the 8.17 Case being reopened?

561
00:32:00,560 --> 00:32:02,280
That case was never closed.

562
00:32:02,280 --> 00:32:03,670
There's no reopening to speak of.

563
00:32:03,670 --> 00:32:04,880
You don't need to hide it from me.

564
00:32:04,880 --> 00:32:05,810
It's been 5 years

565
00:32:05,880 --> 00:32:06,880
with no progress.

566
00:32:07,280 --> 00:32:08,750
It's been a dead end for ages.

567
00:32:08,750 --> 00:32:10,390
What are you snooping around for?

568
00:32:10,390 --> 00:32:11,390
Who told you that?

569
00:32:12,750 --> 00:32:14,210
I don't care how you see me.

570
00:32:15,230 --> 00:32:17,310
I worked my way up
from the security division

571
00:32:17,310 --> 00:32:18,670
just so that someday,

572
00:32:19,210 --> 00:32:21,140
I could solve the 8.17 Case myself.

573
00:32:31,600 --> 00:32:32,120
Fine.

574
00:32:34,030 --> 00:32:35,230
If you're so capable,

575
00:32:35,800 --> 00:32:37,040
go and find out

576
00:32:37,290 --> 00:32:38,350
who this woman was.

577
00:32:39,090 --> 00:32:39,580
Yes.

578
00:32:43,080 --> 00:32:43,720
Sorry for the disturbance.

579
00:32:43,720 --> 00:32:45,120
Thank you for your cooperation.

580
00:32:45,120 --> 00:32:47,390
There are still 31 households
on the east side.

581
00:32:47,390 --> 00:32:48,840
No one has identified the body

582
00:32:48,840 --> 00:32:50,360
and no one has reported a missing person.

583
00:32:50,360 --> 00:32:51,910
This investigation is too difficult.

584
00:32:51,910 --> 00:32:54,150
We don't even know
the victim's identity yet.

585
00:32:54,150 --> 00:32:56,230
Not everyone has someone
who cares about them.

586
00:32:56,230 --> 00:32:58,230
She had neither family nor friends.

587
00:32:58,230 --> 00:32:59,750
Now the only ones who care about her

588
00:32:59,750 --> 00:33:00,750
are us.

589
00:33:01,190 --> 00:33:02,120
Let's continue.

590
00:33:02,600 --> 00:33:04,670
Zhao Ping, your uneven shoulders
are getting worse.

591
00:33:04,670 --> 00:33:05,280
It's fine.

592
00:33:06,950 --> 00:33:07,470
Let's go.

593
00:33:07,470 --> 00:33:09,400
Let's hurry to the next household.

594
00:33:09,470 --> 00:33:09,990
Senior,

595
00:33:10,640 --> 00:33:12,080
your rib injury hasn't fully healed yet.

596
00:33:12,080 --> 00:33:12,810
Take it easy.

597
00:33:15,600 --> 00:33:16,800
The rain is too heavy.

598
00:33:18,320 --> 00:33:19,120
No one's here.

599
00:33:19,840 --> 00:33:21,970
Let's take shelter from the rain here.

600
00:33:27,950 --> 00:33:29,390
This part of the city is too old.

601
00:33:29,390 --> 00:33:30,930
There's not even a single security camera.

602
00:33:30,930 --> 00:33:33,260
I'll report this to the higher-ups later.

603
00:33:43,610 --> 00:33:45,140
What are you doing, Senior?

604
00:33:49,750 --> 00:33:50,350
Zhao Ping.

605
00:33:51,710 --> 00:33:53,310
Isn't this a video doorbell?

606
00:33:54,800 --> 00:33:55,820
Contact the owner.

607
00:33:55,820 --> 00:33:56,270
Okay.

608
00:34:06,640 --> 00:34:08,150
She got out of the taxi

609
00:34:08,600 --> 00:34:10,060
and went toward the river.

610
00:34:10,080 --> 00:34:11,190
These clothes are unmistakable.

611
00:34:10,969 --> 00:34:13,530
[Yu Dan, Investigator, Criminal
Investigation Brigade of Nancheng Branch]

612
00:34:11,870 --> 00:34:13,949
But we can only see the last 2 digits
of the license plate.

613
00:34:13,949 --> 00:34:14,679
The last 2 digits are enough.

614
00:34:14,679 --> 00:34:15,480
I can check it.

615
00:34:21,120 --> 00:34:22,050
Can you check it?

616
00:34:38,030 --> 00:34:39,360
What are you doing here?

617
00:34:41,190 --> 00:34:42,120
Why are you here?

618
00:34:43,280 --> 00:34:44,679
I'm here to find someone.

619
00:34:46,610 --> 00:34:47,409
Find someone?

620
00:34:57,710 --> 00:34:58,920
It's indeed my fault.

621
00:34:58,920 --> 00:34:59,710
I'm sorry.

622
00:35:00,010 --> 00:35:00,960
I forgot to tell you that

623
00:35:00,960 --> 00:35:02,310
I won't be coming home these days.

624
00:35:02,310 --> 00:35:04,310
But you shouldn't come to my workplace.

625
00:35:04,310 --> 00:35:05,480
I was in a meeting.

626
00:35:05,850 --> 00:35:06,910
How embarrassing.

627
00:35:08,520 --> 00:35:10,080
I'm really here to find someone.

628
00:35:10,080 --> 00:35:11,120
Stop kidding.

629
00:35:11,670 --> 00:35:12,480
Who are you looking for?

630
00:35:12,480 --> 00:35:13,000
Senior.

631
00:35:14,670 --> 00:35:15,230
Who is he?

632
00:35:18,750 --> 00:35:19,680
He is...

633
00:35:19,700 --> 00:35:20,700
Professor Jiang.

634
00:35:21,950 --> 00:35:23,580
You're Professor Jiang, right?

635
00:35:23,580 --> 00:35:24,180
Chief Tan.

636
00:35:24,640 --> 00:35:25,450
Hello.

637
00:35:25,640 --> 00:35:26,600
Welcome.

638
00:35:26,970 --> 00:35:27,640
It's great

639
00:35:27,670 --> 00:35:28,800
that you could come.

640
00:35:28,990 --> 00:35:29,520
Please.

641
00:35:32,740 --> 00:35:33,470
Colleagues.

642
00:35:36,270 --> 00:35:37,470
Let me introduce you.

643
00:35:38,750 --> 00:35:39,680
Jiang Hansheng,

644
00:35:39,830 --> 00:35:40,780
Professor Jiang,

645
00:35:40,780 --> 00:35:42,850
is our criminal profiling expert,

646
00:35:42,890 --> 00:35:45,020
Director Wang Pengze's star student.

647
00:35:45,170 --> 00:35:46,100
Professor Jiang

648
00:35:46,270 --> 00:35:47,400
started his career

649
00:35:47,550 --> 00:35:48,460
at the Provincial Department

650
00:35:48,460 --> 00:35:49,540
in the

651
00:35:49,790 --> 00:35:51,120
Crime Research Office.

652
00:35:51,270 --> 00:35:52,190
Currently,

653
00:35:52,310 --> 00:35:53,670
he's working at the Haizhou University
of Political Science and Law

654
00:35:53,670 --> 00:35:54,450
as a professor.

655
00:35:54,450 --> 00:35:56,900
This time,
he's joining us as an external expert

656
00:35:56,900 --> 00:35:58,530
to assist with our precinct's work.

657
00:35:58,530 --> 00:36:00,960
Let's give him a warm welcome.

658
00:36:05,520 --> 00:36:07,380
I'm just an Associate Professor.

659
00:36:08,560 --> 00:36:10,200
Being an Associate Professor is great!

660
00:36:10,200 --> 00:36:11,970
That means you're young.

661
00:36:12,990 --> 00:36:13,810
Come.

662
00:36:13,830 --> 00:36:15,960
Welcome, Associate Professor Jiang.

663
00:36:18,560 --> 00:36:20,090
Continue your discussion.

664
00:36:20,980 --> 00:36:21,940
Associate Professor Jiang,

665
00:36:21,940 --> 00:36:23,270
let's talk in my office.

666
00:36:25,580 --> 00:36:26,240
Wait for me.

667
00:36:30,380 --> 00:36:31,250
Sir.

668
00:36:33,670 --> 00:36:34,600
He's quite good.

669
00:36:40,850 --> 00:36:42,200
He really is good.

670
00:36:42,610 --> 00:36:43,770
What's so good about him?

671
00:36:43,770 --> 00:36:44,700
He's so intense.

672
00:36:44,800 --> 00:36:45,750
Senior, let me tell you.

673
00:36:45,750 --> 00:36:46,760
The way he looked at you wasn't normal.

674
00:36:46,760 --> 00:36:47,480
Who is he?

675
00:36:47,630 --> 00:36:48,520
Didn't they just say?

676
00:36:48,050 --> 00:36:51,490
[Liu Liang, Investigator, Criminal
Investigation Brigade of Nancheng Branch]

677
00:36:48,550 --> 00:36:49,640
He's Professor Jiang Hansheng.

678
00:36:49,640 --> 00:36:50,370
You know him?

679
00:36:50,520 --> 00:36:51,740
Is that what he was asking?

680
00:36:51,740 --> 00:36:53,670
And you call yourself a detective.

681
00:36:54,180 --> 00:36:54,870
Zhou.

682
00:36:56,150 --> 00:36:57,150
Tell us the truth.

683
00:36:57,630 --> 00:36:58,920
Yes, what's going on?

684
00:36:59,120 --> 00:37:00,000
What's happening?

685
00:37:00,000 --> 00:37:01,120
Senior, tell us about it.

686
00:37:01,120 --> 00:37:01,480
I...

687
00:37:01,480 --> 00:37:02,480
Who is he?

688
00:37:02,750 --> 00:37:03,480
Oh, give it a rest.

689
00:37:03,480 --> 00:37:04,230
You talk too much.

690
00:37:04,230 --> 00:37:04,790
No, he...

691
00:37:04,790 --> 00:37:05,830
Found it!

692
00:37:06,640 --> 00:37:09,040
[Bai Yang, Technician, Criminal
Investigation Brigade of Nancheng Branch]

693
00:37:09,390 --> 00:37:13,900
[Shangyue Hotel]

694
00:37:16,650 --> 00:37:18,860
[Wan Chongshan, Investigator, Criminal
Investigation Brigade of Nancheng Branch]

695
00:37:22,510 --> 00:37:23,300
Same car,

696
00:37:23,520 --> 00:37:24,640
same physical characteristics,

697
00:37:24,640 --> 00:37:25,770
and the same outfit.

698
00:37:25,870 --> 00:37:26,870
The time was

699
00:37:26,890 --> 00:37:27,890
July 23rd, night,

700
00:37:28,020 --> 00:37:29,050
10:57 PM.

701
00:37:29,080 --> 00:37:31,250
The time of death was
early morning on the 24th.

702
00:37:31,250 --> 00:37:32,720
This means for some reason,

703
00:37:32,720 --> 00:37:34,600
she left the hotel late at night,

704
00:37:34,600 --> 00:37:36,640
took a car to the Tong River riverbank,

705
00:37:36,640 --> 00:37:37,720
and was shot to death.

706
00:37:37,720 --> 00:37:39,000
After being killed, her body was dumped

707
00:37:39,000 --> 00:37:39,600
and carried downstream.

708
00:37:39,600 --> 00:37:40,750
Then, on July 27th,

709
00:37:41,600 --> 00:37:43,060
a swimmer discovered her.

710
00:37:43,560 --> 00:37:44,350
That guy was so scared that

711
00:37:44,350 --> 00:37:45,950
he still can't get out of bed.

712
00:37:49,360 --> 00:37:51,840
[Shangyue Hotel]

713
00:38:31,660 --> 00:38:32,660
Jiang Hansheng.

714
00:38:41,190 --> 00:38:42,190
Professor Jiang.

715
00:38:48,260 --> 00:38:50,520
It's the gun from the 8.17 Case, isn't it?

716
00:38:54,150 --> 00:38:55,120
Director Lu said

717
00:38:55,890 --> 00:38:57,750
you'd understand once you saw it.

718
00:38:58,360 --> 00:38:59,150
He was right.

719
00:39:00,290 --> 00:39:02,090
Is Zhou Jin working on this case?

720
00:39:02,190 --> 00:39:05,050
She's now responsible for
identifying the victim.

721
00:39:11,740 --> 00:39:13,830
If I don't go, I won't feel at ease.

722
00:39:14,330 --> 00:39:15,660
Your senior is on one side,

723
00:39:15,660 --> 00:39:17,140
and Mr. Wan is on the other.

724
00:39:17,310 --> 00:39:18,600
What are you worried about?

725
00:39:18,600 --> 00:39:20,060
Just take me to one of them.

726
00:39:21,480 --> 00:39:22,190
No way.

727
00:39:22,600 --> 00:39:24,200
Your injury has just healed.

728
00:39:24,380 --> 00:39:25,870
At this rate, you'll end up like me.

729
00:39:25,870 --> 00:39:27,000
I injured my back years ago,

730
00:39:27,000 --> 00:39:28,920
and it still hurts whenever it rains.

731
00:39:28,920 --> 00:39:31,440
Don't take your youth for granted.

732
00:39:32,040 --> 00:39:33,330
It takes 100 days to recover
from bone injuries.

733
00:39:33,330 --> 00:39:34,960
Can we continue
after you've fully recovered?

734
00:39:34,960 --> 00:39:35,810
Stop arguing with me.

735
00:39:35,810 --> 00:39:37,040
Focus on getting well.

736
00:39:37,040 --> 00:39:37,620
That's what matters most.

737
00:39:37,620 --> 00:39:38,150
Zhou Jin.

738
00:39:51,120 --> 00:39:51,680
Hello.

739
00:39:53,150 --> 00:39:54,550
Hello, Professor Jiang.

740
00:39:59,010 --> 00:39:59,870
This is my wife.

741
00:40:05,830 --> 00:40:07,090
What a perfect couple!

742
00:40:07,140 --> 00:40:09,580
Zhou Jin and Professor Jiang are married.

743
00:40:09,830 --> 00:40:11,150
I'm aware of that.

744
00:40:12,010 --> 00:40:13,070
That's wonderful.

745
00:40:13,120 --> 00:40:13,580
Indeed.

746
00:40:13,650 --> 00:40:14,310
Good.

747
00:40:14,310 --> 00:40:15,020
I need to get back to work.

748
00:40:15,020 --> 00:40:16,540
It's my bad.

749
00:40:16,570 --> 00:40:17,490
Everyone's been so busy lately,

750
00:40:17,490 --> 00:40:19,490
I didn't have time to break the news.

751
00:40:20,470 --> 00:40:23,030
Our marriage was also quite sudden.

752
00:40:23,280 --> 00:40:26,120
How could something
as important as marriage be so sudden?

753
00:40:26,120 --> 00:40:27,850
You could have at least told us.

754
00:40:28,670 --> 00:40:29,870
It was indeed sudden.

755
00:40:30,820 --> 00:40:31,410
Sir.

756
00:40:31,770 --> 00:40:33,500
Can I also go to Shangyue Hotel?

757
00:40:33,730 --> 00:40:35,990
I want to confirm the victim's identity.

758
00:40:36,920 --> 00:40:37,400
Well...

759
00:40:37,450 --> 00:40:38,050
Chief Tan.

760
00:40:38,640 --> 00:40:39,770
Can I accompany her?

761
00:40:40,440 --> 00:40:41,440
Of course you can.

762
00:40:41,830 --> 00:40:42,830
I got you this badge

763
00:40:42,830 --> 00:40:44,270
to help you with the investigation.

764
00:40:44,270 --> 00:40:44,800
However,

765
00:40:45,000 --> 00:40:46,150
we'll have to trouble you

766
00:40:46,150 --> 00:40:47,010
with this trip.

767
00:40:48,830 --> 00:40:49,360
Zhou Jin.

768
00:40:50,230 --> 00:40:51,440
I'd like a private word with you

769
00:40:51,440 --> 00:40:52,480
about this case.

770
00:40:53,440 --> 00:40:53,920
Sure.

771
00:40:56,520 --> 00:40:58,040
What were you talking about just now?

772
00:40:58,040 --> 00:41:00,300
Does Chief Tan have instructions for me?

773
00:41:04,000 --> 00:41:05,060
It's not Chief Tan.

774
00:41:05,160 --> 00:41:05,680
It's me.

775
00:41:06,720 --> 00:41:07,270
Zhou Jin.

776
00:41:07,800 --> 00:41:09,230
You have no experience confronting

777
00:41:09,230 --> 00:41:10,750
the people behind the 8.17 Case.

778
00:41:10,750 --> 00:41:11,920
Their past actions

779
00:41:12,180 --> 00:41:14,690
prove they have strong
provocative tendencies.

780
00:41:14,690 --> 00:41:15,930
When provocation fails,

781
00:41:15,930 --> 00:41:16,970
revenge follows.

782
00:41:17,750 --> 00:41:19,150
New leads are good,

783
00:41:19,810 --> 00:41:21,410
but we must remain vigilant.

784
00:41:21,460 --> 00:41:22,260
I understand.

785
00:41:23,160 --> 00:41:23,990
That group of people

786
00:41:23,990 --> 00:41:26,190
has no respect for the police or the law.

787
00:41:27,000 --> 00:41:29,460
That's why my brother
suffered so terribly.

788
00:41:30,350 --> 00:41:31,150
Get in the car.

789
00:41:39,750 --> 00:41:41,080
I haven't asked you yet.

790
00:41:41,670 --> 00:41:42,730
What exactly do you

791
00:41:42,960 --> 00:41:43,960
teach at school?

792
00:41:45,320 --> 00:41:46,050
Psychology.

793
00:41:46,520 --> 00:41:48,180
Specifically, which branch?

794
00:41:49,310 --> 00:41:50,310
Don't tell me it's

795
00:41:50,780 --> 00:41:52,040
criminal psychology?

796
00:41:52,400 --> 00:41:52,870
It is.

797
00:41:54,340 --> 00:41:56,220
I was afraid you wouldn't
want to work with someone

798
00:41:56,220 --> 00:41:58,350
in the same field, so I didn't tell you.

799
00:41:58,790 --> 00:41:59,390
It's fine.

800
00:41:59,800 --> 00:42:00,960
You're not on the front line,

801
00:42:00,960 --> 00:42:02,890
so I guess you're half a colleague.

802
00:42:04,250 --> 00:42:05,420
But you never told me

803
00:42:05,850 --> 00:42:08,120
that you worked
at the provincial department before.

804
00:42:08,120 --> 00:42:09,920
What else are you hiding from me?

805
00:42:10,690 --> 00:42:11,870
Back then, your family and the matchmaker

806
00:42:11,870 --> 00:42:13,330
had several requirements

807
00:42:13,400 --> 00:42:14,860
that I didn't really meet.

808
00:42:15,330 --> 00:42:15,930
Like what?

809
00:42:17,190 --> 00:42:18,040
Having both parents alive,

810
00:42:18,040 --> 00:42:19,240
a harmonious family,

811
00:42:19,310 --> 00:42:20,640
and a nine-to-five job.

812
00:42:21,370 --> 00:42:22,310
What kind of requirements are those?

813
00:42:22,310 --> 00:42:22,910
It's okay.

814
00:42:23,600 --> 00:42:25,660
I'll keep covering for you with them.

815
00:42:26,270 --> 00:42:26,870
So,

816
00:42:27,450 --> 00:42:28,530
what do you expect

817
00:42:28,750 --> 00:42:29,730
from a partner?

818
00:42:35,710 --> 00:42:36,310
Zhou Jin,

819
00:42:38,150 --> 00:42:39,880
I hope you won't get hurt again.

820
00:42:48,430 --> 00:42:49,230
In the future,

821
00:42:49,400 --> 00:42:51,130
I'll definitely face dangers.

822
00:42:51,960 --> 00:42:53,800
But the more dangerous a place is,

823
00:42:53,800 --> 00:42:56,000
the greater the opportunity it offers.

824
00:42:56,070 --> 00:42:57,730
Don't worry, Jiang Hansheng.

825
00:42:58,000 --> 00:42:59,270
I'll definitely take good care of myself.
